```{r include=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
data_new <- read.csv(file = "./Data/SecondStep_most_up_to_date.csv") 
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = FALSE, message = FALSE, warning = FALSE)
cal_func <- function(x, y) {
  m1 <- lm(y ~ x, data_new)
  summary(m1)
  }
```
